snippet.title: MotoGP™25 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Rev up the Heart of Racing with #MotoGP25 on April 30th. 🏍️ Experience the 2025 championship with official riders, tracks, and exciting new features like Training Sessions, the Arcade Experience, Full Cross-play, and more. Get ready for the ultimate #MotoGP thrill

📘Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/motoGPVideogame

📱 Discord: https://discord.com/invite/S47gpx5vE2
🌍 Website: https://motogpvideogame.com/
